<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: sans-serif; color: #1f2937; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }
    h1 { font-size: 20px; color: #6b7280; }
    ul { line-height: 1.8; }
    p { line-height: 1.6; }
    .footer { margin-top: 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Service No Longer Available</h1>
  <p>We regret to inform you that a service you had a booking for is no longer available:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Business:</strong> {{businessName}}</li>
    <li><strong>Service:</strong> {{serviceName}}</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We apologise for the inconvenience. Please visit the Qulene app to explore other available services.</p>
  <p class="footer">Qulene &mdash; Waitlist &amp; Appointment Manager</p>
</body>
</html>
